      Fields in org.safs.tools.logs.processor with type parameters of type Tag 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      protected java.util.Stack<Tag> XMLSaxToJUnitHandler.tagStack
      The stack contains the tag currently being processed.
      The tag will be pushed into the stack at the end of XMLSaxToJUnitHandler.startElement(String, String, String, Attributes), and it will be popped out at the begin of XMLSaxToJUnitHandler.endElement(String, String, String).
      The pushed/popped Tag can very probable be null if we don't map a XML tag into Java class.
